---
import { BaseLayout } from "@walle/layouts";
---

<BaseLayout
  headerTitle="Privacy Policy"
  headerDescription="Read our privacy policy to learn how we handle your data."
  headerRobots="noindex, nofollow"
>
  <main class="container prose">
    <section class="page-header">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Last updated: May 6, 2025</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <p>
      This notice describes how European OpenSource (<a
        href="https://europeanopensource.eu/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener">europeanopensource.eu</a
      >) collects and processes users’ personal data through the use of Piwik PRO, exclusively for
      anonymous and aggregated statistical analysis purposes.
    </p>

    <h4>1. Data Controller</h4>
    <p>
      The data controller is the European OpenSource collective. For any privacy-related requests,
      you can contact us at:<br />
      <code>support</code> \[@\] <code>europeanopensource</code> \[.\] eu
    </p>

    <h4>2. Data Collected</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Personal data:</strong> We do not collect personal data from users visiting the site.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Anonymous statistical data:</strong> We collect only anonymous and aggregated data for
        statistical analysis, in order to improve content and browsing experience. This data does not
        allow direct or indirect identification of site visitors.
      </li>
      <li>
        Piwik PRO may collect the following information: Operating system and browser type, Country,
        Browsing activity (pages visited, session duration, referrer), technical and analytics
        cookies.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h4>3. Purpose and Legal Basis of Processing</h4>
    <p>
      Processing is based on the user’s consent, pursuant to Art. 6(1)(a) GDPR. Upon first access to
      the site, consent is requested via a banner; if consent is not given, data is not collected.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Statistical analysis on site usage.</li>
      <li>Improvement of the services offered.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>4. Cookies</h4>
    <p>
      The site may use technical and/or anonymous analytics cookies (e.g., cookies for aggregated
      and anonymous statistical analysis). No profiling or marketing cookies are used.
    </p>

    <h4>5. Data Recipients</h4>
    <p>
      The collected data is not shared with third parties. It is not transmitted to sub-processors
      or third parties and is not used by Piwik PRO for its own purposes. Data is retained for a
      maximum of 14 months.
    </p>

    <h4>6. Users’ Rights</h4>
    <p>
      Since no personal data is collected, it is not possible to identify users or exercise rights
      related to personal data (such as access, rectification, or deletion). Consent can be
      withdrawn at any time via browser settings or the cookie banner.
    </p>

    <h4>7. Changes to the Privacy Policy</h4>
    <p>This notice may be updated at any time. Changes will be published on this page.</p>

    <p>
      For further information or questions about privacy, please contact us using the contact
      details available on the site.
    </p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
